org.resthub.core.context.config

Interface ResthubBeanDefinitionParser

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.xml.BeanDefinitionParser
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractEntitesParser, AbstractJAXBElementsParser, AbstractParser, DatabaseDescriptorDefinitionParser, ExcludeEntitiesParser, ExcludeJAXBElementsParser, IncludeEntitiesParser, IncludeJAXBElementsParser, InitializeDatabaseBeanDefinitionParser

    public interface ResthubBeanDefinitionParser
extends org.springframework.beans.factory.xml.BeanDefinitionParser
    This interface must be implemented by any BeanDefinitionParser to be autodetected by ResthubNamespaceHandler. Additionnaly, The implementing class must be declared in META-INF/services/org.resthub.core.context.config.ResthubBeanDefinitionParser file
